  <p>That was the short list, if we get long I would also attribute the profound change in my art work to the past teachers and mentors I met at CSU summer arts in 2014 and 2015. They're amazing photographers, and wonderful teachers who opened up art as a possibility for me. Nicole J. Hill, Doug Dertinger, Holly Andres, David H. Wells, Erika Gentry, David Hilliard. Above are images from the first session, and below are a few from the second.</p>




























  
    
      

        

        
          
            
